Subject: [PATCH] xen-blkback: set ring->xenblkd to NULL after kthread_stop()
Patch-mainline: v5.10.4
References: openEuler-21.03

stable inclusion
from stable-5.10.4
commit aadd67750f43132177138fcd56ebc60aeb06228a
bugzilla: 46903

